### 移动端登录接口测试

### 1. 用户名登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/auth/app-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginType": "USERNAME",
  "username": "foundationyuanma",
  "password": "buzhidao",
  "deviceType": "MOBILE_ANDROID",
  "deviceId": "android_device_123456"
}

### 2. 手机号登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/auth/app-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginType": "MOBILE",
  "mobile": "13800138000",
  "password": "buzhidao",
  "deviceType": "MOBILE_IOS",
  "deviceId": "ios_device_789012"
}

### 3. 邮箱登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/auth/app-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginType": "EMAIL",
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "buzhidao"
}

### 4. 移动端专用登录接口
POST {{baseUrl}}/app/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginType": "USERNAME",
  "username": "foundationyuanma",
  "password": "buzhidao"
} 